    'services.hero.digitalSolutions': 'digital solutions',
    'services.hero.description': 'From captivating websites and high-converting landing pages to comprehensive branding and SEO optimization - we craft digital experiences that drive results. Our end-to-end solutions ensure your online presence works as hard as you do.',
