    // Community Page
    'community.hero.title': 'Upvista Community',
    'community.hero.subtitle': 'An open source place where developers, designers, engineers from all around the world collaborate, learn, recognize, grow and even earn.',
    'community.vision.title': 'Our Vision',
    'community.vision.p1': 'We envision a global ecosystem where technology professionals from every corner of the world can come together to create, innovate, and transform ideas into reality. The Upvista Community is more than just a platform—it\'s a movement that breaks down geographical barriers and creates opportunities for meaningful collaboration.',
    'community.vision.p2': 'Our community thrives on the principle that great ideas can come from anywhere, and by connecting brilliant minds across continents, we can solve complex challenges and build the future of technology together.',
    'community.philosophy.title': 'Open Source Philosophy',
    'community.philosophy.p1': 'At the heart of our community lies a deep commitment to open source principles. We believe that knowledge should be freely shared, code should be collaborative, and innovation should be accessible to everyone. This philosophy drives everything we do—from the tools we build to the projects we support.',
    'community.philosophy.p2': 'Our open source approach means that every contribution matters, every idea is valued, and every member has the opportunity to shape the direction of our community. Whether you\'re contributing code, documentation, design, or simply sharing your expertise, you\'re helping build something greater than any individual could create alone.',
    'community.collaboration.title': 'Global Collaboration',
    'community.collaboration.p1': 'The Upvista Community brings together talented individuals from diverse backgrounds, cultures, and skill sets. From seasoned industry veterans to passionate newcomers, from frontend designers to backend engineers, from AI researchers to DevOps specialists—our community represents the full spectrum of technology expertise.',
    'community.collaboration.p2': 'Through our global network, members can find collaborators for projects, mentors for guidance, and peers for knowledge sharing. Time zones become opportunities rather than obstacles, as our community operates 24/7 with members contributing from every continent.',
    'community.collaboration.p3': 'We celebrate the diversity of perspectives that comes from our international membership, recognizing that the best solutions often emerge from the intersection of different experiences and viewpoints.',
    'community.learning.title': 'Learning & Growth',
    'community.learning.p1': 'Continuous learning is the foundation of personal and professional growth in our community. We provide multiple pathways for skill development, from informal knowledge sharing sessions to structured learning programs, from peer-to-peer mentoring to expert-led workshops.',
    'community.learning.p2': 'Our members are encouraged to step out of their comfort zones, explore new technologies, and challenge themselves with projects that push the boundaries of their expertise. Whether you\'re learning your first programming language or mastering the latest AI frameworks, our community provides the support and resources you need to succeed.',
    'community.learning.p3': 'We believe that growth happens not just through individual effort, but through the collective wisdom of our community. Every question asked, every problem solved, and every insight shared contributes to the learning journey of all our members.',
    'community.recognition.title': 'Recognition & Earning',
    'community.recognition.p1': 'We believe that valuable contributions deserve recognition and reward. Our community provides multiple avenues for members to earn from their skills and expertise, from freelance opportunities within the network to collaborative projects that generate revenue for all participants.',
    'community.recognition.p2': 'Recognition in our community goes beyond monetary rewards. We celebrate achievements through peer recognition, showcase exceptional work in our portfolio, and provide opportunities for members to build their professional reputation within the technology industry.',
    'community.recognition.p3': 'Whether you\'re looking to supplement your income, build a freelance career, or simply gain recognition for your contributions, the Upvista Community provides the platform and opportunities to help you achieve your goals.',
    'community.join.title': 'Join Our Community',
    'community.join.p1': 'The Upvista Community is open to anyone with a passion for technology and a desire to collaborate, learn, and grow. Whether you\'re a student just starting your journey, a seasoned professional looking to share your expertise, or an entrepreneur seeking collaborators for your next big idea, there\'s a place for you here.',
    'community.join.p2': 'By joining our community, you become part of a global movement that\'s shaping the future of technology. You\'ll have access to a network of talented professionals, opportunities for collaboration and earning, and a platform to showcase your work and grow your reputation.',
    'community.join.p3': 'Together, we\'re building more than just software—we\'re building connections, opportunities, and a community that empowers everyone to reach their full potential in the digital world.',
    
